<p>The calendar shows:<br>
A segment under every reserved days with a border <b><font color="#ff0000">red</font></b> for those ones confirmed or <b><font color="#00ff00">green</font></b> for those ones which will expire after seven days if they are not confirmed.<br><b>CLICK on it to see more details of the reservation.</b></p><p>Click on <b>NEW</b> for a new reservation.</p>
<p>Click on the button on the top/right <b>Logout</b>  to exit.</p>
